The method should return an integer representing the maximum number of tasks that can be completed.
Other requirements:
Each worker can only be assigned to a single task.
Each worker must have a strength greater than or equal to the task's strength requirement.
Each worker can receive at most one magical pill.
The magical pill will increase a worker's strength by the value of `strength`.
The method should assign the magical pills and tasks in a way that maximizes the number of completed tasks.
